WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.680
Merry Christmas, everybody!

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:03.080
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:03.800
Day 64.

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:11.047
I have Diana here with me today, and we just wanted to come on today and tell you all Merry Christmas.

00:00:13.313 --> 00:00:14.968
We love you all so much.

00:00:14.968 --> 00:00:16.393
Thank you for your support.

00:00:17.502 --> 00:00:27.474
We appreciate all of you coming out every day to these videos to pray with us and intercede for the nations.

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:37.266
Your support and love are so appreciated—praying for my daughter, for our family, and for me.

00:00:38.910 --> 00:00:46.490
The emails have been so kind lately, and I love the people sending earmuffs for Megan for the sound.

00:00:47.444 --> 00:00:55.120
A lot of times she won't wear those because she doesn't like things on her head, but we're getting there.

00:00:55.291 --> 00:00:58.760
We're just believing God she's going to be completely healed in 2024.

00:00:58.760 --> 00:01:03.080
We're closing this thing out, believing for the complete manifestation of Megan.

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:06.195
She holds her ears like that throughout the day.

00:01:06.520 --> 00:01:10.711
For all of you who are so considerate, I know you're doing it out of love.

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:13.560
It's just a habit, I think.

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:18.520
Of course, the earmuffs are so nice, so we're going to try them.

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:25.674
Sometimes you wonder if it was just the brand that she hasn't liked in the past, so she'll wear them for short periods.

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:29.000
Thank you all for helping my Megan out.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.146
What a blessing!

00:01:30.911 --> 00:01:34.853
So many people reaching out and trying to help.

00:01:35.044 --> 00:01:37.556
I just wanted to say thank you that you care.

00:01:39.375 --> 00:01:46.379
There are just a lot of kind, wonderful people on here with such great hearts.

00:01:47.279 --> 00:01:48.179
Thank you.

00:01:49.595 --> 00:01:51.379
I believe the best is yet to come.

00:01:51.379 --> 00:01:55.340
2025 is coming and I'm anticipating great things.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.559
We want to show you this real quick.

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:05.888
My wife went to the grocery store and got this cake.

00:02:07.147 --> 00:02:12.863
It's green, so I don't want it to disappear behind the green screen, but it says 'Happy Birthday Jesus.

00:02:12.863 --> 00:02:24.571
' We try every year to throw Jesus a birthday party with brownies or cookies, and this year Diana found a 'Happy Birthday Jesus' cake from the grocery store.

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:34.889
It even has a manger on it.

00:02:39.675 --> 00:02:45.625
We'll sing happy birthday to Him as a family and do a full-blown birthday party for Him.

00:02:45.970 --> 00:02:49.020
He is our Lord and Savior.

00:02:49.265 --> 00:02:53.867
We wanted to come on and tell you all a very Merry Christmas.

00:02:53.867 --> 00:03:02.635
We're going to take communion with you, so if you want to get your communion ready, we're going to lift up the name of Jesus.

00:03:02.990 --> 00:03:04.765
Let's lift up the body.

00:03:05.867 --> 00:03:12.648
His body was broken and beaten for all our transgressions and iniquities.

00:03:12.648 --> 00:03:17.810
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, you're healed.

00:03:19.053 --> 00:03:35.223
In this Christmas season, it's even more of a gift to believe for your divine healing and to believe that everything broken in your body has been healed and made whole by His stripes.

00:03:35.223 --> 00:03:39.759
No matter what it is, nothing's too big and nothing's too small.

00:03:39.759 --> 00:03:42.840
Jesus paid the price for it all.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:52.074
According to Galatians, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law, and the curse of the law is everything in Deuteronomy 28.

00:03:52.651 --> 00:04:01.371
I believe that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever, and that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:04:01.686 --> 00:04:14.040
This beautiful Christmas day, where all the gifts are being poured out on loved ones, Jesus gave the gift of His life.

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:27.249
He came as a child born in a manger and wrapped in swaddling clothes as a gift for humanity.

00:04:27.724 --> 00:04:36.435
He died for every single one of us so that we don't have to have all the bondage of this earth.

00:04:36.435 --> 00:04:39.759
He came to set the captives free.

00:04:39.995 --> 00:04:45.496
The angels sang, 'Glory to God in the highest, peace on earth, goodwill to men.

00:04:45.496 --> 00:04:56.440
' Hallelujah, because of what He did on this very special day, Jesus paid the price.

00:04:56.440 --> 00:05:01.391
He lived 33 years and died on the cross after He was born.

00:05:01.743 --> 00:05:03.152
Oh, what a plan!

00:05:03.856 --> 00:05:08.156
What an amazing God we serve.

00:05:08.156 --> 00:05:15.753
He came to set the captives free and gave the ultimate sacrifice.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:23.039
Thank you, Father, for giving Your Son.

00:05:23.039 --> 00:05:27.125
Thank you, Lord, for this body that was broken and beaten for us.

00:05:27.470 --> 00:05:39.617
Thank you for communion, that we are joint-heirs with You and we're able to be seated with You in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:05:39.617 --> 00:05:47.540
We have dominion and authority over all satanic agendas.

00:05:47.540 --> 00:05:57.526
Father, I thank You that You said nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:07.800
We take this body right now in the name of Jesus and we say, 'Happy Birthday, Jesus.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:15.808
' Thank You for this communion and for what You did for us.

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:27.149
Thank You for coming to this earth as a baby.

00:06:42.714 --> 00:06:43.183
We don't have to be bound by sickness anymore.

00:06:43.183 --> 00:06:45.559
Now, Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:06:47.405 --> 00:06:55.491
You said it was the cleansing flow that washed us as white as snow.

00:06:55.491 --> 00:06:58.400
It took care of all that sin and You made us spotless before You.

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:08.480
Father, we thank You for that beautiful blood that flowed on Calvary's tree.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:12.534
It flowed down and cleansed Diana and me, and it cleansed every single one of you.

00:07:12.534 --> 00:07:15.862
We're so grateful for Your life and Your blood.

00:07:18.830 --> 00:07:37.959
We thank You, Lord, that as we confess our sins, You are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:07:37.959 --> 00:07:52.765
He's written our names in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:07:52.765 --> 00:08:06.759
It's Your blood that sets us free.

00:08:06.759 --> 00:08:39.326
By the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony, we take this blood in the name of Jesus.

00:08:51.945 --> 00:09:15.968
We give You praise, Father, for Your presence and the anointing of the Holy Spirit.

00:09:37.700 --> 00:09:42.510
We love You and we magnify You.

00:09:42.510 --> 00:09:46.519
Happy birthday to You, dear Jesus!

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:56.620
One day we'll celebrate His birthday with Him in person; I look forward to that.

00:10:02.089 --> 00:10:02.347
We honor the Lord today.

00:10:02.347 --> 00:10:07.498
Thank You for all You've done for us this year.

00:10:07.498 --> 00:10:21.800
Thank You for President Trump and the new administration coming in, giving us another opportunity and a season of grace.

00:10:21.800 --> 00:10:36.306
Sister Billye talked about the gifts being distributed on the 25th, and we believe something supernatural has happened today.

00:10:37.515 --> 00:10:48.520
We pray you felt His presence in your house today as you're spending time with your loved ones.

00:10:48.520 --> 00:10:58.140
Maybe you're alone, but you are not alone because we are with you.

00:10:58.140 --> 00:11:04.620
If you don't have any family, we are your family.

00:11:04.620 --> 00:11:19.510
Diana, Braden, and I are loving on you through the camera, telling you that you've got what it takes.

00:11:19.510 --> 00:11:26.302
Jesus has a plan for your life.

00:11:26.302 --> 00:11:41.217
You may feel alone in the natural, but there's somebody in a little house in Oklahoma believing God with you.

00:11:41.217 --> 00:11:48.742
2025 is going to be an amazing year for you.

00:11:48.742 --> 00:12:01.886
Like we always say, Diana, put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:12:01.886 --> 00:12:08.180
There are good days ahead for the body of Christ.

00:12:08.180 --> 00:12:13.753
We had a lady send us a letter.

00:12:13.753 --> 00:12:20.852
She is alone, her husband has passed, and her little canary passed away recently.

00:12:20.852 --> 00:12:26.086
She's having a hard time, and her letter was so touching.

00:12:26.086 --> 00:12:35.126
There are so many people going through so much right now.

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:54.920
Even the loss of a little bird matters; she wanted to know if it would be in heaven because she misses her friend.

00:12:57.500 --> 00:13:04.080
I promised I wasn't going to cry, but it really touched me.

00:13:04.080 --> 00:13:15.349
William Branham talked about this before he went home to be with the Lord.

00:13:15.349 --> 00:13:20.959
Sister Billye told us this story.

00:13:20.959 --> 00:13:40.493
If an animal was precious to you on this earth, God has so much compassion and love for us that those animals are waiting for you in heaven.

00:13:47.085 --> 00:13:57.227
The Lord showed William Branham that those animals, even during the Rapture, are so important to you that they are going to be taken too.

00:13:57.227 --> 00:14:18.720
He gives you the desires of your heart, and if it's your desire to have your pet with you, the Lord's going to see to it.

00:14:21.000 --> 00:14:23.291
He cares about the smallest details in your life.

00:14:33.124 --> 00:14:33.519
He has it all figured out.

00:14:33.519 --> 00:14:50.625
I believe the little parakeets, sparrows, and even a little 'Peanut the pocket squirrel' like Bob Ross used to carry—God cares about them.

00:14:50.625 --> 00:14:56.760
I'll never forget when my dog died when I was Braden's age.

00:14:58.703 --> 00:15:11.666
It meant so much to me and hurt so bad at the time, but I gave it over to the Lord.

00:15:15.940 --> 00:15:35.879
When I heard the testimony from Billye while we were sitting around the table talking about the Rapture, we were all rejoicing over the fact that soon and very soon, we're about to go see the King.

00:15:48.983 --> 00:15:49.297
Our loved ones and our loved animals are going to come right alongside us.

00:15:49.297 --> 00:16:00.458
William Branham saw many amazing things before he went to be with the Lord.

00:16:06.216 --> 00:16:10.333
He even saw egg-shaped cars in the 1940s and 50s that were driving themselves, like Teslas.

00:16:16.093 --> 00:16:24.417
He said when Jesus comes back, what the Lord showed him in that vision is that a woman would be running the White House.

00:16:24.417 --> 00:16:35.062
Everybody thought it was Kamala Harris he was seeing, but it wasn't time yet.

00:16:35.062 --> 00:16:39.600
Who's coming in 2028?

00:16:56.390 --> 00:16:56.780
I don't know, but it would be neat if that vision lines up.

00:16:56.780 --> 00:17:01.639
God has a plan for everything.

00:17:01.639 --> 00:17:10.269
He wants you to be filled with joy, not dread or anxiety.

00:17:11.129 --> 00:17:17.662
We are looking up, for our redemption is drawing nigh, folks.

00:17:17.662 --> 00:17:26.433
In 2025, we're not just going to survive; we're going to thrive.

00:17:36.850 --> 00:17:40.846
In 2024, the Lord told me I would soar and there would be a great open door, and it has been exactly that.

00:17:40.846 --> 00:17:49.110
We have gone from glory to glory this year.

00:17:49.110 --> 00:17:55.000
I'm believing 2025 will be a supernatural year of God's provision.

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:56.262
Heaven on Earth!

00:17:56.262 --> 00:18:00.120
I'm believing for healings, demonstrations, and manifestations.

00:18:00.120 --> 00:18:04.702
There's going to be a great harvest of souls.

00:18:05.271 --> 00:18:13.685
I want to give you all hope to get excited about the days ahead.

00:18:27.559 --> 00:18:28.420
We pray this video blessed you.

00:18:41.080 --> 00:18:41.400
We thank You, Lord, for healing, wholeness, and wellness over every household.

00:18:46.571 --> 00:18:48.228
We pray they'll hear Your voice concerning investments.

00:18:52.210 --> 00:18:54.440
The Holy Spirit will lead and guide you into all things.

00:18:54.440 --> 00:19:07.800
You're going to know them by their fruit, and you're not going to be led astray in these last days.

00:19:07.800 --> 00:19:23.435
I pray for discernment over your minds today, that the inward voice of the Holy Spirit would be so loud.

00:19:23.435 --> 00:19:27.759
You'll know exactly what to do.

00:19:27.759 --> 00:19:38.829
You're free from addictions, from cigarettes and alcohol to gambling, pornography, and lust.

00:19:50.607 --> 00:19:50.853
You are bound no more by those demonic strongholds.

00:19:50.853 --> 00:19:56.137
You're not bound by depression or anxiety.

00:20:05.315 --> 00:20:05.937
We believe for promotions, raises, bonuses, and growth in businesses.

00:20:06.248 --> 00:20:15.849
We believe every seed you sowed in 2024, you're going to reap in 2025 exceedingly and abundantly.

00:20:15.849 --> 00:20:24.440
Thank You, Father, for children and for marriages being restored.

00:20:24.440 --> 00:20:33.060
We pray over President Trump as he has a beautiful Christmas.

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:47.540
We thank You that no more wars are caused while the current administration is in the White House.

00:20:47.540 --> 00:20:59.440
We call peace over Russia and the Ukraine deal and over our southern borders.

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:02.309
2025 will be an amazing year.

00:21:02.309 --> 00:21:10.023
If you're new here, please subscribe and click that notification bell.

00:21:10.023 --> 00:21:19.417
We're creating a Vietnam channel, a Chinese channel, a South Korean channel, a Russian channel, and a Philippines channel.

00:21:19.417 --> 00:21:26.536
We're doing it by the grace of God and through your support.

00:21:26.536 --> 00:21:30.771
The links are in the description.

00:21:30.771 --> 00:21:38.090
Asia is going to catch on fire for Jesus!

00:21:38.090 --> 00:21:43.039
Tomorrow is Diana's birthday, the 26th.

00:21:43.039 --> 00:21:49.120
It always made her feel special being so close to Jesus's birthday.

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:52.102
She's still young at heart.

00:21:52.102 --> 00:22:01.520
We've made it through a lot, and we keep going.

00:22:11.409 --> 00:22:11.564
God is good.

00:22:11.564 --> 00:22:17.559
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:22:29.035 --> 00:22:29.340
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

00:22:29.340 --> 00:22:30.889
Merry Christmas!
